file: AfterToolCallHookInterface.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Contract\\Hook\\AfterToolCallHookInterface"
type: interface
summary: Defines the contract for processing events after a tool execution completes within the agent core. It enables decoupled post-processing logic by providing context and cancellation support for the result.
